    "Appendix Table A2 presents the analyses by putting all the packages together, with Python and Rust language packages as treated packages and the rest as controls.",
    "The results are qualitatively and quantitatively similar to those in Table 3.",
    "relative to GitHub Copilot's introduction, with \"0\" designating its launch.",
    "The turquoise line represents the trend for the treated group (Python packages in panel A; Rust packages in panel B) in the post-treatment period.",
    "The shaded red area delineates the trend for the synthetic control group, which is a weighted combination of control packages used to construct the counterfactual scenario."
